name: Conscious Growth 102h
description:
A creative collaboration by gneural and Cacheflowe, Conscious Growth 102h is part of a series of snapshots from the duo's Conscious Growth interactive digital mural in Snowmass, CO. Every image in this series is an individual moment in the Conscious Growth generative timeline, never to be repeated.

Conscious Growth is a hybrid of gneural's traditional, freehand art and Cacheflowe's creative coding, brought together through the magic of custom software. The combination of these disciplines merges traditional, hand-drawn illustration and generative digital art.

Format: 5400 x 7200px PNG file, suitable for printing at 18x24 inches
